    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [170ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and add the <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give it a good stir – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>green lentils</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
