      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>cornflour </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Crack in the<strong> egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>and beat together with a fork</p><p>Add the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>,<strong> half</strong> the<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>white sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't worry if it looks a bit grainy for now!</p>",
      "order": 5,
