    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have caramelised, add the<strong> tomato stock</strong>, <strong>drained lentils</strong> and<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened to a pasta sauce consistency – this is your <strong>veg sauce</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
