            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Layer <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>veg sauce</strong> over the bottom of an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then top with a layer of <strong>courgette ribbons</strong></p><p>Layer the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>veg sauce </strong>on top and top with another layer of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>courgette ribbons</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>white sauce</strong>, sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>lighter Mediterranean veg lasagne</strong></p>",
