    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the<strong> lighter Mediterranean veg lasagne</strong> from the oven and leave to stand for a few min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>rocket</strong> to the side and drizzle over a little<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
